The '''''Null Space''''' was a [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] [[DP20 gunship/Legends|DP20 gunship]]. It was commanded by the [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]], [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Obigon]], and his crew including [[H'Krav]] and [[Meekeef]]. The ''Null Space'' was surrendered to [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Zero-G assault stormtrooper]]s to avoid a fight.

